            "text": "which is essential to handle customer complaints . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "parent": 3,
            "text": "These models contain common problem categories , typical customer issues and their solutions , greeting styles . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "parent": 3,
            "text": "Currently these models are manually created over time . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "Towards this , ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "parent": 0,
            "text": "we propose an unsupervised technique ",
            "relation": "ROOT"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
