            "text": "which still results in high word error rates ( 40 % ) ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 13,
            "parent": 14,
            "text": "and show ",
            "relation": "ATTRIBUTION"
        },
        {
            "id": 14,
            "parent": 10,
            "text": "that even from these noisy transcriptions of calls we can automatically build a domain model . <S>",
            "relation": "CAUSE-RESULT-REASON"
        },
        {
            "id": 15,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "The domain model is comprised of primarily a topic taxonomy ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 16,
            "parent": 15,
            "text": "where every node is characterized by topic ( s ) , typical Questions-Answers ( Q&As ) , typical actions and call statistics . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 17,
            "parent": 18,
            "text": "We show ",
            "relation": "ATTRIBUTION"
        },
        {
            "id": 18,
